INTO ME WITH THAT!

13:18.999 --> 13:21.034
LILY, TAKE ALL THAT
STUFF BACK TO THE CAR.

13:21.068 --> 13:22.936
DAD, CAN YOU JUST
STOP BEING SO SELFISH?

13:22.970 --> 13:25.939
ALL RIGHT? YOU'RE
RUINING THE MOST
PRECIOUS DAY OF...

13:25.973 --> 13:28.075
WHAT'S-HER-NAME'S LIFE.

13:28.108 --> 13:29.476
YES, SWEETIE, SEE,

13:29.509 --> 13:31.178
YOUR DAD'S BEEN THINKING
ABOUT THIS A LOT,

13:31.211 --> 13:32.980
AND HE'S CONCERNED
THAT YOUR DNA,

13:33.013 --> 13:34.214
WHICH YOU INHERITED
FROM ME,

13:34.247 --> 13:37.284
IS CAUSING YOU TO HAVE
THE HOT PANTS FOR DEAN.

13:37.517 --> 13:40.253
WHAT?! I DON'T HAVE
THE HOT PANTS FOR DEAN.

13:40.287 --> 13:44.024
