YOU LIKE HIM.

13:46.994 --> 13:50.097
EW! I--I DO NOT
LIKE HIM.

13:50.130 --> 13:51.999
MAN, I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU PULLED
ALL THIS STUFF

13:52.032 --> 13:55.035
BECAUSE SHE'S GOT
THE HOT PANTS
FOR THE KID.

13:55.068 --> 13:56.203
NO! NO, NO, NO, NO!

13:56.236 --> 13:59.372
I DON'T, OK?
I HATE HIM!

14:01.141 --> 14:03.143
SORRY, BUD,
BUT, UH...

14:03.176 --> 14:04.978
YOU'RE NOT
WANTED HERE.

14:05.012 --> 14:06.179
RIGHT,
WHO ARE YOU?

14:06.213 --> 14:08.982
I'M LILY'S BOYFRIEND.

14:09.016 --> 14:12.252
HA HA! HE IS NOT
MY BOYFRIEND.

14:12.285 --> 14:14.087
YEAH,
SHE LOVES YOU.

14:14.121 --> 14:17.057
NO, I DON'T!

14:17.090 --> 14:18.025
SEE? NOW GET
OUT HERE!

14:18.058 --> 14:21.528
DOES SOMEBODY WANT TO GET
BAND GEEK OFF OF ME?

14:21.561 --> 14:23.230
OH, YOU'D LIKE THAT
WOULDN'T YOU?

14:23.263 --> 14:25.198
YOU WANT A PIECE
OF ME?

14:25.232 --> 14:28.168
JUST GET THE HELL
OUT OF HERE!

14:29.102 --> 14:32.039
RUN AWAY, LOSER!

14:32.072 --> 14:33.673
AAH!

14:33.706 --> 14:37.510
[DRUM BANGING
AND CRASHING]

14:37.544 --> 14:40.280
Brad: I-I'M OK, LILY!

14:41.381 --> 14:45.185
A-A-A-AAH!

14:45.552 --> 14:49.089
HEH HOO! BABY, SOME DAY
YOU ARE GONNA HAVE TO

14:49.122 --> 14:51.158
