WITH ALL THIS, OK?

14:51.191 --> 14:52.559
GIRLS LIKE BOYS.
MM-HMM.

14:52.592 --> 14:54.427
SOMETIMES GIRLS FALL
IN LOVE WITH BOYS.

14:54.461 --> 14:55.428
