* REUNITED, HEY--HEY!

20:51.418 --> 20:53.320
HIT IT!

21:00.393 --> 21:01.961
* REUNITED

21:01.994 --> 21:03.563
* AND IT FEELS SO GOOD

21:03.596 --> 21:05.332
* REUNITED

21:05.365 --> 21:06.799
* 'CAUSE WE UNDERSTOOD

21:06.833 --> 21:08.568
* REUNITED

21:08.601 --> 21:09.869
