21:23.516 --> 21:24.351
* REUNITED

21:24.384 --> 21:26.619
* BABY,
I LOVE YOUR-- *

21:26.653 --> 21:29.822
* REUNITED, HEY, HEY,
HEY, HEY, HEY *

21:29.856 --> 21:32.559
* REUNITED, OY,
OY, OY, OY *

