LIKE I WAS GOING
THAT FAST.

21:42.469 --> 21:46.506
RUNNING AROUND
THE ENTIRE BLOCK
IN 6 SECONDS?

21:46.539 --> 21:48.408
NO HUMAN
COULD DO THAT.

21:48.441 --> 21:50.343
I LOVE
BEING A ROBOT.

21:50.377 --> 21:51.177
IS LILY HOME?

21:51.210 --> 21:54.681
I DON'T KNOW. I'LL USE
MY X-RAY VISION.

21:54.714 --> 21:55.448
NOPE.

21:55.482 --> 21:56.383
ALL RIGHT, I'LL JUST
RING THE BELL.

21:56.416 --> 21:59.652
HEY, BRAD,
I'M GONNA RUN
AROUND THE BLOCK.

21:59.686 --> 22:02.689
